title: Should the Anti Pump-Dump-Exist Whales systeme be removed in the next V3 (MoonratX)?
body: For a big BNB reward pool, we need a lot of volume (buy and sell). But this Anti Pump-Dump-Exist Whales systeme can't get us a big amount of volume per day. So the BNB pool grow, but slowly. If the Anti Pump-Dump-Exist Whales systeme was removed, there will be a lot more volume, so the bnb pool will grow faster, and also, a lot of big pump. The price can't pump now, because of this anti-whales system. And also, people who are trying to buy over 100B and don't know this anti-whales system, they think that they are unable to buy SMRAT and they just don't buy if they don't read.
author: 0x35Ae2Bd1507751EA5CB34208F5D74cFE6B6E5f8B
